This directory (test_Ar_multiple_models_c) contains a test that computes the
energy of a perfect Ar FCC crystal and a finite cluster as a function of
lattice spacing for two models. The test uses the NEIGH-RVEC-F NBC and locator
or iterator mode.

Makefile                           -- makefile to compile and build executables with
                                      GNU or Intel compilers
README                             -- this file 
test_Ar_multiple_models_c.c        -- Code for the test
test_Ar_multiple_models_c.kim      -- KIM descriptor file for the test

